This paper deals with the computation of eigenvectors, which is a fundamental problem in numerical linear algebra and is used in various applications related to artificial intelligence, machine learning, and system identification simulations. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.NA (Numerical Analysis), followed by cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), and cs.SY (Systems and Control).
